{"tid":2439571,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"愛國獲回報 梁競徽拍抗日cult片做男一","createTime":"2021-03-09T10:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T10:57:09.000Z","uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"673fe386297efc635aa82da070eaf7197a386748","tid":2439571,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛國當然有回報，梁競徽(唯唯)過去時常發表愛國言論，邀他擔任抗日片男主角，絕對有說服力。早前唯唯到橫店拍攝了一部抗日cult片《浴血狂蟒》，他在微博上載照片留言道︰「是日拍攝完成～回去梳洗～非常開心可以參與這次拍攝～中國軍人～就是牛！保家衛國！這是我們的使命。」而預告片段亦已可在抖音中看到。<br />\n<br />\n據網上資料顯示，此片以1945年發生的緬北滇西反攻戰為背景，故事提到中國應英方要求，派了一支遠征軍入緬對抗日軍。戰鬥中，有三架飛虎隊戰機被日軍擊落在雲南原始森林大娘山中，而日本研究的生化武器在叢林中泄露，導致一條巨蟒變異，劇情相當離奇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JNeXzg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJNeXzg8.jpg&h=7c969224&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"637ab10cf7107ac50c7e22b906347bd5b241b4ec","tid":2439571,"uid":301050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:47:24.000Z","msg":"點解個題材咁好可以打最中意打嘅日本仔唔打<br />\n搵條蛇嚟打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25c95920bacf61fdefd2c8004cdee4ec3fc2f40","tid":2439571,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>愛國是生意</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6633f4e947f85174e2998a87d4e23380923a05da","tid":2439571,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"反送中英雄竟然有得拍抗日片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833bd03657abd7f8db78d744c5d89c18efb23392","tid":2439571,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeece667b3ccee6c0c79958548430d9fe256f2cf","tid":2439571,"uid":168138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/scD100W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FscD100W.jpg&h=b32934b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f58c090d4c7eb84678126b1c03af5acca9e9d4a6","tid":2439571,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"中國應英方要求，派了一支遠征軍入緬對抗日軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />